>> tags: spizing, italian

Take a whole cleaned @fish{1%kg}. Make incisions in her skin.

Rub the fish inside and out with @Italian Spice Mix{}, @salt, @olive oil{} and juice of @lemon{1}.

Optionally, add fresh @dill and sliced @lemon{1} to the fish.

Bake in a preheated 180 degree #oven for about ~{25%minutes} or until done.
